{"tid":823904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(信則有) 官媒：港珠澳大橋颱風下一切正常 核電廠穩定","createTime":"2018-09-17T01:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T08:06:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5403671001afd5e5a8e2cda1daca20f3d6b7a40a","tid":823904,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:50:10.000Z","msg":"內地傳媒報導，港珠澳大橋在在超強颱風「山竹」吹襲期間「一切正常」。<br />\n<br />\n報導指，在超強颱風山竹登陸前的16時41分，港珠澳大橋氣像監測系統顯示橋區降雨類型為大暴雨，風速40m/s（13級）。全線供配電系統高低壓運行正常，各泵狀態正常。大橋監控信息顯示大橋安全、正常，監控數據顯示橋上測到最大風速55m/s（16級），索力、位移、震動監測都在設計範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中國廣核集團發布消息稱，中廣核大亞灣、陽江、台山、防城港核電基地以最嚴要求嚴陣以待，確保颱風過境期間機組狀態保持安全穩定。目前中廣核四大核電基地的機組均保持安全穩定的狀態，前線工作人員也平安。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thinkhk.com/article/2018-09/17/29549.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2018-09%2F17%2F29549.html&d=KPPkmUstXgKNlaWvbQeyJl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=7741095e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thinkhk.com/article/2018-09/17/29549.html</a>"},{"pid":"9e7d96138aea0e30432cf7f534c55cee1da9ba47","tid":823904,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:54:02.000Z","msg":"仆街了"},{"pid":"fd4d5728dac86d4ce838612271c9d5f75328e737","tid":823904,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e7d96138aea0e30432cf7f534c55cee1da9ba47","tid":823904,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:54:02.000Z","msg":"仆街了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfbdb132060a429067d81cc97f0072d5f01e444","tid":823904,"uid":54264,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/5517000712738ae25efe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp9.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2F5517000712738ae25efe&h=5444824c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be4e681611154e25cdeacbd2c6f66b303